Class BlogMining

  • java.lang.Object
    • BlogMining

  • public class BlogMining
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provides a CLi for the blog mining app It allows a person to interact with the application by passing pot url, post id, blod id etc. to crawl the wordPress blogs. It also has various utility functions to crawl the post.
